# Cloud Scraper Admin Panel

This project scrapes quotes from [quotes.toscrape.com](https://quotes.toscrape.com), stores them in MongoDB Atlas, and displays them in a web admin panel.

- "Scrape Now" button triggers real-time scraping
- Backend built with Flask and BeautifulSoup
- Frontend built with Next.js
- Data stored in MongoDB Atlas
- Backend hosted on Render, frontend on Vercel

